OL,3,CWRU to cut number of professional
OL,4,Csides to three
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union is set to
OL,7,Fannounce it will cut the number of
OL,8,Fprofessional club sides in Wales from
OL,9,Ffour to three as soon as possible.
OL,11,FAt a press conference, WRU chair
OL,12,FRichard Collier-Keywood expressed his
OL,13,Fdesire for the change to happen by
OL,14,Fnext season, but accepts that pace of
OL,15,Fchange may not be possible.
OL,17,FIt is the Unions ambition that they
OL,18,Freach three times by consent - which
OL,19,Fcould include two teams merging - but
OL,20,Fsay it will go out to a tender process
OL,21,Fif no agreement is reached.
