OL,3,CWRU to cut number of professional
OL,4,Csides to three
OL,6,FIt is currently unclear what the
OL,7,Fidentity of the three teams will be,
OL,8,Fbut it is understood that there will
OL,9,Fbe one based in Cardiff, one in East
OL,10,FWales and one in West Wales.
OL,12,FIn August, the WRU said that radical
OL,13,Fchange was needed to save the game
OL,14,Ffrom its steady decline.
OL,16,FToday, after a furious backlash from
OL,17,Fplayers and supporters, they were
OL,18,Fforced to retreat from that position
OL,19,Fsomewhat.
