OL,3,CWRU to cut number of professional
OL,4,Csides to three
OL,6,FThe optimal solution proposed by new
OL,7,FDirector of Rugby Dave Reddin was
OL,8,Fhalving the number of professional
OL,9,Fteams in Wales, consolidating top
OL,10,Ftalent and resources into two clubs.
OL,12,FBut after a consultation process, the
OL,13,FUnion has alighted on three teams.
OL,15,FCollier-Keywood said a substantial
OL,16,Fnumber of stakeholders involved in the
OL,17,Fconsultation process agreed that three
OL,18,Fteams was the way forward.
