OL,3,CWRU to cut number of professional
OL,4,Csides to three
OL,6,FIt is unlikely this change will go
OL,7,Fthrough in time or next season. So the
OL,8,Ffour clubs will likely continue next
OL,9,Fyear but there will be unequal funding.
OL,11,FThe Dragons and Cardiff will receive
OL,12,Fmore funding than the Ospreys and
OL,13,FScarlets by virtue of the fact that
OL,14,Fthey signed the new financial
OL,15,Fagreement with the WRU.
OL,17,FThe two West Wales clubs refused to
OL,18,Fsign the new deal due to a lack of
OL,19,Fguarantees surrounding the Union
OL,20,Frescuing Cardiff from administration.
